Use this prompt for the Json schema, because it will often leave some rows out of the
    schema with AI :
Below is the schema I am going to use for recipes, please take note of how 
there are 3 different types of instructions 'en' for english, 'sk' for slovak
and 'jp' for japanese, please translate each recipe, also note that there is a
'nutritional information' section and a 'notes' section for any additional notes,
also, please make the 'recipeType' be _ for the folowing recipes, take
the text recipe I give you and return to me a .json that works in this schema :